headline: CrowdStrike Delivers Unified Data Protection for the AI Era
summary: AUSTIN, Texas, September 18, 2025--Fal.Con 2025, Las Vegas – CrowdStrike (NASDAQ: CRWD) today announced new Falcon® Data Protection innovations that deliver real-time, unified security built for how data moves in the AI era. By addressing the rising risks of GenAI data leaks, insider threats, and sensitive data in motion across hybrid environments, CrowdStrike is defining the future of data protection and driving consolidation of legacy, fragmented tools at scale.
